WEBVTT

00:00:06.112 --> 00:00:07.114
[rock music]

00:00:07.114 --> 00:00:15.197
♪ ♪

00:00:21.309 --> 00:00:23.013
[woman singing in Japanese]

00:00:23.013 --> 00:00:29.626
♪ ♪

00:01:41.704 --> 00:01:43.741
&gt;&gt; narrator: THIS IS THE TALE OF

00:01:43.741 --> 00:01:45.578
A MAN WHO CONTINUES TO SEARCH

00:01:45.578 --> 00:01:47.549
FOR HIS OWN PATH EVEN AS FATE

00:01:47.549 --> 00:01:49.620
BETRAYS HIM.

00:01:49.620 --> 00:01:51.489
AS A RESULT OF HIS ACTIONS,

00:01:51.489 --> 00:01:53.126
SIMON IS THROWN INTO PRISON

00:01:53.126 --> 00:01:54.228
AS A WAR CRIMINAL.

00:01:54.228 --> 00:01:56.800
HE FINDS WAITING FOR HIM THERE

00:01:56.800 --> 00:01:58.470
HIS FORMER ENEMY, VIRAL.

00:01:58.470 --> 00:02:01.242
ELSEWHERE, ROSSIU IS INFORMED

00:02:01.242 --> 00:02:02.746
THAT THE MOON’S IMPACT WILL DEAL

00:02:02.746 --> 00:02:05.518
A FATAL BLOW TO EARTH.

00:02:05.518 --> 00:02:07.254
AMIDST THE BATTLE,

00:02:07.254 --> 00:02:08.189
THE ARC‐GURREN DEPARTS,

00:02:08.189 --> 00:02:09.793
ABANDONING A GREAT MANY PEOPLE

00:02:09.793 --> 00:02:11.462
AS IT LIFTS OFF.

00:02:11.462 --> 00:02:13.333
BUT NIA, WHO HAS BECOME

00:02:13.333 --> 00:02:14.468
THE ANTI‐SPIRALS’ MESSENGER,

00:02:14.468 --> 00:02:17.575
REVEALS MORE DREADFUL NEWS.

00:02:17.575 --> 00:02:19.245
&gt;&gt; Nia: EVEN IF THEY DO ESCAPE

00:02:19.245 --> 00:02:20.581
INTO SPACE, THE ONLY THING

00:02:20.581 --> 00:02:21.750
AWAITING THEM IS DESPAIR.

00:02:21.750 --> 00:02:23.888
&gt;&gt; Simon: WHAT DID YOU SAY?

00:02:23.888 --> 00:02:25.257
&gt;&gt; Yoko: SO I DON’T SEE YOU FOR

00:02:25.257 --> 00:02:26.827
A WHILE, AND YOU HAVE TO GO AND

00:02:26.827 --> 00:02:29.566
TURN INTO A REAL BORING BITCH,

00:02:29.566 --> 00:02:34.509
NIA.

00:02:34.509 --> 00:02:35.745
&gt;&gt; Nia: SURRENDER TO THE

00:02:35.745 --> 00:02:36.647
INEVITABLE.

00:02:36.647 --> 00:02:39.352
HUMANITY HAS NO FUTURE.

00:02:39.352 --> 00:02:44.495
&gt;&gt; Simon: HEY, WAIT!

00:02:44.495 --> 00:02:45.698
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: HOW MANY WERE ABLE

00:02:45.698 --> 00:02:46.432
TO BOARD?

00:02:46.432 --> 00:02:49.438
&gt;&gt; Kinon: 176,800 CONFIRMED.

00:02:49.438 --> 00:02:50.474
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: LESS THAN HALF OF

00:02:50.474 --> 00:02:51.543
WHAT WE’D PLANNED.

00:02:51.543 --> 00:02:52.712
&gt;&gt; Cybela: ENEMY DETECTED!

00:02:52.712 --> 00:02:54.348
TWO MUGANN, HUGE ONES!

00:02:54.348 --> 00:02:58.323
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: NO WAY!

00:02:58.323 --> 00:03:01.162
WAS THIS A TRAP ALL ALONG?

00:03:12.217 --> 00:03:15.290
[chirping]

00:03:29.485 --> 00:03:30.387
[Kunpa laughs]

00:03:30.387 --> 00:03:31.389
&gt;&gt; Naakim: GIVE IT BACK!

00:03:31.389 --> 00:03:32.424
&gt;&gt; Kunpa: YOU WANT IT SO MUCH,

00:03:32.424 --> 00:03:33.527
TAKE IT BACK!

00:03:33.527 --> 00:03:34.930
LOOK AT YOU.

00:03:34.930 --> 00:03:38.537
YOU’RE SUCH A BABY!

00:03:38.537 --> 00:03:39.973
[bell chiming]

00:03:39.973 --> 00:03:40.708
&gt;&gt; Kunpa: OH!

00:03:40.708 --> 00:03:42.211
LET’S GO!

00:03:42.211 --> 00:03:42.779
&gt;&gt; Geki: WE’RE LATE!

00:03:42.779 --> 00:03:47.221
WE’RE LATE!

00:03:47.221 --> 00:03:48.423
&gt;&gt; Maosha: I TELL YOU WHAT,

00:03:48.423 --> 00:03:49.693
NAAKIM, YOU’RE HOPELESS.

00:03:49.693 --> 00:03:50.728
COME ON.

00:03:50.728 --> 00:03:51.395
LET’S GO.

00:03:51.395 --> 00:03:51.864
GET UP.

00:03:51.864 --> 00:03:53.534
&gt;&gt; Yoko: WAIT.

00:03:53.534 --> 00:03:58.309
&gt;&gt; Maosha: OH!

00:03:58.309 --> 00:03:59.412
&gt;&gt; Yoko: YOU CAN GET UP BY

00:03:59.412 --> 00:04:04.488
YOURSELF, CAN’T YOU?

00:04:04.488 --> 00:04:07.227
THAT’S BETTER, LITTLE MAN.

00:04:07.227 --> 00:04:09.365
&gt;&gt; Naakim: OH.

00:04:14.308 --> 00:04:15.545
&gt;&gt; Maosha: OH!

00:04:15.545 --> 00:04:17.649
[grumbles]

00:04:17.649 --> 00:04:19.285
&gt;&gt; Principal: LISTEN UP, CLASS.

00:04:19.285 --> 00:04:20.621
I WOULD LIKE TO INTRODUCE YOU

00:04:20.621 --> 00:04:21.957
ALL TO YOUR NEW TEACHER.

00:04:21.957 --> 00:04:23.359
&gt;&gt; Geki: I HEAR SHE’S FROM

00:04:23.359 --> 00:04:24.295
THE MAINLAND!

00:04:24.295 --> 00:04:25.363
&gt;&gt; Kunpa: SHE’S A TOTAL BABE!

00:04:25.363 --> 00:04:26.934
&gt;&gt; Maosha: NAH, SHE’S NOT

00:04:26.934 --> 00:04:28.436
ALL THAT PRETTY.

00:04:28.436 --> 00:04:29.606
&gt;&gt; Naakim: SHE’S OUR

00:04:29.606 --> 00:04:30.508
NEW TEACHER!

00:04:30.508 --> 00:04:32.512
&gt;&gt; Yoko: I’M YOMAKO.

00:04:32.512 --> 00:04:33.781
I HOPE WE CAN ALL

00:04:33.781 --> 00:04:34.950
BECOME FRIENDS.

00:04:34.950 --> 00:04:37.889
[children singing]

00:04:37.889 --> 00:04:39.024
&gt;&gt; Principal: I’M TERRIBLY SORRY

00:04:39.024 --> 00:04:40.962
ABOUT ALL THE JUNK IN HERE.

00:04:40.962 --> 00:04:43.032
IT USED TO BE A NIGHT GUARD HUT,

00:04:43.032 --> 00:04:45.337
SO AT LEAST IT’S LIVABLE.

00:04:45.337 --> 00:04:46.272
&gt;&gt; Yoko: THANK YOU FOR

00:04:46.272 --> 00:04:47.007
EVERYTHING.

00:04:47.007 --> 00:04:48.376
&gt;&gt; Principal: WE CALL THIS

00:04:48.376 --> 00:04:49.846
A SCHOOL, BUT I’M THE ONLY ONE

00:04:49.846 --> 00:04:50.815
ON STAFF.

00:04:50.815 --> 00:04:52.284
SO I GOTTA TELL YOU, IT’S A BIG

00:04:52.284 --> 00:04:53.721
RELIEF TO HAVE SOME NEW BLOOD

00:04:53.721 --> 00:04:54.990
HERE, TRULY.

00:04:54.990 --> 00:04:55.992
&gt;&gt; Yoko: YOU’RE VERY KIND.

00:04:55.992 --> 00:04:57.795
&gt;&gt; Principal: STILL, I CAN’T

00:04:57.795 --> 00:04:59.298
HELP BUT WONDER WHY SOMEONE AS

00:04:59.298 --> 00:05:00.635
FAMOUS AS YOU WOULD WANNA COME

00:05:00.635 --> 00:05:03.874
TO OUR LITTLE ISLAND.

00:05:03.874 --> 00:05:04.943
&gt;&gt; Yoko: YOU SURE YOU HAVEN’T

00:05:04.943 --> 00:05:06.547
MISTAKEN ME FOR SOMEONE ELSE?

00:05:06.547 --> 00:05:07.849
I’M JUST MISS YOMAKO,

00:05:07.849 --> 00:05:09.920
AN ORDINARY NEW SCHOOLTEACHER.

00:05:09.920 --> 00:05:11.523
&gt;&gt; Principal: OH, YES, YES.

00:05:11.523 --> 00:05:12.892
WE OLD‐TIMERS TEND TO BLURT

00:05:12.892 --> 00:05:13.594
THINGS OUT.

00:05:13.594 --> 00:05:15.765
&gt;&gt; girl: BYE, TEACHER! BYE‐BYE!

00:05:15.765 --> 00:05:18.604
&gt;&gt; boy: BYE, NEW TEACHER LADY!

00:05:18.604 --> 00:05:20.073
&gt;&gt; Yoko: THOSE CHILDREN ARE

00:05:20.073 --> 00:05:21.577
THE FIRST CHILDREN TO BE BORN

00:05:21.577 --> 00:05:23.547
ON THE SURFACE.

00:05:23.547 --> 00:05:24.783
I WANT TO BE THE ONE WHO

00:05:24.783 --> 00:05:26.954
WATCHES OVER THEM.

00:05:26.954 --> 00:05:27.989
&gt;&gt; Principal: ME TOO.

00:05:27.989 --> 00:05:29.058
I DON’T WANT THEM TO HAVE TO

00:05:29.058 --> 00:05:30.761
LIVE THEIR LIVES WITHOUT THE

00:05:30.761 --> 00:05:34.068
SKY ABOVE THEM.

00:05:37.474 --> 00:05:39.078
&gt;&gt; Naakim: WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

00:05:39.078 --> 00:05:40.046
&gt;&gt; Kunpa: LET ME HAVE A LOOK!

00:05:40.046 --> 00:05:41.583
&gt;&gt; Naakim: NO! FORGET IT!

00:05:41.583 --> 00:05:46.527
[class gasps]

00:05:46.527 --> 00:05:47.494
[Yoko chuckles]

00:05:47.494 --> 00:05:50.735
&gt;&gt; class: OH!

00:05:50.735 --> 00:05:53.406
&gt;&gt; Yoko: PLAYTIME!

00:05:53.406 --> 00:05:58.349
&gt;&gt; class: ONE, TWO, THREE, FOUR!

00:05:58.349 --> 00:05:59.886
&gt;&gt; Yoko: QUIT BEING SO FUSSY!

00:05:59.886 --> 00:06:03.059
&gt;&gt; Kunpa: AH!

00:06:03.059 --> 00:06:09.906
[class laughing]

00:06:09.906 --> 00:06:15.383
&gt;&gt; class: MISS YOMAKO!

00:06:15.383 --> 00:06:16.553
&gt;&gt; Yoko: UNTIL SIX YEARS AGO,

00:06:16.553 --> 00:06:17.822
HUMANS LIVED THEIR WHOLE LIVES

00:06:17.822 --> 00:06:19.559
UNDERGROUND.

00:06:19.559 --> 00:06:21.062
THE TWO WHO SET US ALL FREE

00:06:21.062 --> 00:06:23.499
WERE KAMINA AND SIMON,

00:06:23.499 --> 00:06:26.707
THE GREAT HEROES.

00:06:26.707 --> 00:06:28.009
&gt;&gt; Naakim: HEY, ISN’T THAT‐‐

00:06:28.009 --> 00:06:28.911
&gt;&gt; Maosha: HUH?

00:06:28.911 --> 00:06:29.813
&gt;&gt; Naakim: ISN’T THAT OUR

00:06:29.813 --> 00:06:30.548
TEACHER?

00:06:30.548 --> 00:06:31.617
&gt;&gt; Maosha: AW, COME ON.

00:06:31.617 --> 00:06:32.852
NO WAY.

00:06:32.852 --> 00:06:36.125
[class shuddering]

00:06:36.125 --> 00:06:37.160
&gt;&gt; Yoko: NO CHATTING.

00:06:37.160 --> 00:06:38.797
YOU KNOW THAT.

00:06:38.797 --> 00:06:41.102
&gt;&gt; Maosha: [grumbles]

00:06:41.102 --> 00:06:44.074
WHY AM I BEING PUNISHED?

00:06:44.074 --> 00:06:46.980
[bell chiming]

00:06:46.980 --> 00:06:48.984
&gt;&gt; Maosha: MORNING, EVERYONE!

00:06:48.984 --> 00:06:51.088
[students laughing]

00:06:51.088 --> 00:06:54.796
&gt;&gt; Naakim: GOOD MORNING, EVERY‐‐

00:06:54.796 --> 00:06:56.132
OH!

00:06:56.132 --> 00:06:57.568
&gt;&gt; Maosha: JUST IGNORE IT.

00:06:57.568 --> 00:06:58.837
IT ONLY MAKES IT WORSE WHEN YOU

00:06:58.837 --> 00:07:00.073
LET THEM GET TO YOU LIKE THAT.

00:07:00.073 --> 00:07:02.444
&gt;&gt; Naakim: OH!

00:07:02.444 --> 00:07:03.413
&gt;&gt; Yoko: OH?

00:07:03.413 --> 00:07:05.751
&gt;&gt; Naakim: THIS IS A LIE!

00:07:05.751 --> 00:07:07.120
A BIG, FAT LIE!

00:07:07.120 --> 00:07:09.458
&gt;&gt; Maosha: HMPH!

00:07:18.076 --> 00:07:19.613
&gt;&gt; Naakim: AH, MY BAG!

00:07:19.613 --> 00:07:21.550
WHO THE HECK PUT IT UP THERE?!

00:07:21.550 --> 00:07:22.819
&gt;&gt; Kunpa: AH, QUIT BAWLING!

00:07:22.819 --> 00:07:23.854
IT’S JUST A STUPID BAG!

00:07:23.854 --> 00:07:26.793
&gt;&gt; Naakim: MY DAD GAVE ME THAT

00:07:26.793 --> 00:07:27.629
BEFORE HE DIED!

00:07:27.629 --> 00:07:28.964
IT’S ALL I HAVE TO REMEMBER

00:07:28.964 --> 00:07:31.503
HIM BY!

00:07:31.503 --> 00:07:32.538
&gt;&gt; Kunpa: JUST CLIMB UP THERE

00:07:32.538 --> 00:07:33.607
AND GET IT YOURSELF!

00:07:33.607 --> 00:07:34.509
&gt;&gt; Maosha: NO, DON’T!

00:07:34.509 --> 00:07:35.544
I’LL GET IT FOR‐‐

00:07:35.544 --> 00:07:36.445
&gt;&gt; Naakim: ALL RIGHT, THEN!

00:07:36.445 --> 00:07:37.949
I’LL GO GET IT!

00:07:37.949 --> 00:07:39.886
&gt;&gt; WHAT ARE YOU SAYING?

00:07:39.886 --> 00:07:41.222
&gt;&gt; YOU CAN’T! DON’T DO IT!

00:07:41.222 --> 00:07:42.090
&gt;&gt; IT’S TOO DANGEROUS!

00:07:42.090 --> 00:07:44.495
[Maosha panting]

00:07:44.495 --> 00:07:45.898
&gt;&gt; Yoko: MAOSHA?

00:07:45.898 --> 00:07:48.537
&gt;&gt; Maosha: TEACHER, IT’S NAAKIM!

00:07:48.537 --> 00:07:51.543
[Naakim grunting]

00:07:51.543 --> 00:07:52.745
&gt;&gt; Yoko: NAAKIM, NO!

00:07:52.745 --> 00:07:53.547
&gt;&gt; Principal: YOU SHOULDN’T

00:07:53.547 --> 00:07:54.649
CALL OUT TO HIM!

00:07:54.649 --> 00:07:56.520
HE MAY LOSE HIS CONCENTRATION.

00:07:56.520 --> 00:07:58.089
&gt;&gt; Yoko: BUT WHY IN THE WORLD

00:07:58.089 --> 00:07:59.224
IS HE‐‐

00:07:59.224 --> 00:08:00.761
&gt;&gt; Principal: THAT BAG IS

00:08:00.761 --> 00:08:02.598
A MEMENTO FROM HIS FATHER.

00:08:02.598 --> 00:08:05.103
THREE YEARS AGO, NAAKIM AND HIS

00:08:05.103 --> 00:08:06.807
MOTHER CAME HERE TO THIS ISLAND,

00:08:06.807 --> 00:08:08.176
WHERE HIS MOTHER WAS BORN,

00:08:08.176 --> 00:08:12.050
BUT HE NEVER REALLY FIT IN.

00:08:12.050 --> 00:08:17.060
[all gasp]

00:08:17.060 --> 00:08:22.739
[all sigh]

00:08:22.739 --> 00:08:24.241
&gt;&gt; Naakim: GOT IT!

00:08:24.241 --> 00:08:28.617
OHH. AAH!

00:08:28.617 --> 00:08:30.120
&gt;&gt; Yoko: DON’T LOOK DOWN!

00:08:30.120 --> 00:08:35.196
[students gasp]

00:08:35.196 --> 00:08:35.965
&gt;&gt; Principal: WOULD YOU LOOK

00:08:35.965 --> 00:08:39.773
AT THAT.

00:08:39.773 --> 00:08:42.110
&gt;&gt; Naakim: TEACHER.

00:08:42.110 --> 00:08:43.614
&gt;&gt; Yoko: THAT WAS CRAZY.

00:08:43.614 --> 00:08:45.584
&gt;&gt; Naakim: I KNOW, BUT MY DAD

00:08:45.584 --> 00:08:47.555
GAVE ME THIS.

00:08:47.555 --> 00:08:49.926
I HATE THIS ISLAND.

00:08:49.926 --> 00:08:51.997
I HATE IT, ’CAUSE DAD

00:08:51.997 --> 00:08:54.001
ISN’T HERE.

00:08:54.001 --> 00:08:57.107
BUT I DO THINK THIS VIEW IS

00:08:57.107 --> 00:08:59.646
REALLY PRETTY.

00:08:59.646 --> 00:09:02.084
&gt;&gt; Yoko: YOU KNOW, I SAW A VIEW

00:09:02.084 --> 00:09:05.558
LIKE THIS ONCE BEFORE.

00:09:05.558 --> 00:09:06.960
I WAS WITH A BOY WHO WAS A LOT

00:09:06.960 --> 00:09:08.664
LIKE YOU.

00:09:08.664 --> 00:09:10.601
&gt;&gt; Naakim: LIKE ME?

00:09:10.601 --> 00:09:11.870
&gt;&gt; Yoko: THAT’S RIGHT.

00:09:11.870 --> 00:09:13.206
I MADE A WHOLE BUNCH OF NEW

00:09:13.206 --> 00:09:14.576
FRIENDS BACK THEN.

00:09:14.576 --> 00:09:15.945
WE DID ALL KINDS OF THINGS,

00:09:15.945 --> 00:09:17.715
ALWAYS WORKING HARD FOR

00:09:17.715 --> 00:09:19.552
A BETTER TOMORROW.

00:09:19.552 --> 00:09:20.554
THERE WERE ALSO SOME PEOPLE

00:09:20.554 --> 00:09:22.057
WHO DIED, THOUGH.

00:09:22.057 --> 00:09:24.328
&gt;&gt; Naakim: OH.

00:09:24.328 --> 00:09:25.731
&gt;&gt; Yoko: YOU SHOULD REMEMBER

00:09:25.731 --> 00:09:27.635
YOUR FATHER AS BEST AS YOU CAN.

00:09:27.635 --> 00:09:29.171
IT DOESN’T MATTER HOW.

00:09:29.171 --> 00:09:30.741
JUST MAKE SURE YOU HOLD ON TO

00:09:30.741 --> 00:09:34.214
HIM TIGHT IN YOUR HEART, OKAY?

00:09:34.214 --> 00:09:36.586
[students cheering]

00:09:36.586 --> 00:09:37.855
&gt;&gt; Maosha: HEY!

00:09:37.855 --> 00:09:40.828
&gt;&gt; Kunpa: ARE YOU OKAY?

00:09:40.828 --> 00:09:41.963
&gt;&gt; Yoko: SO DO YOU HATE

00:09:41.963 --> 00:09:43.166
EVERYONE HERE?

00:09:43.166 --> 00:09:44.602
&gt;&gt; Naakim: UH‐UH.

00:09:44.602 --> 00:09:44.936
[chuckles]

00:09:44.936 --> 00:09:47.007
[students all talking]

00:09:49.979 --> 00:09:51.650
&gt;&gt; Kunpa: THAT WAS AWESOME.

00:09:51.650 --> 00:09:52.852
&gt;&gt; Naakim: IT WAS?

00:09:52.852 --> 00:09:53.887
&gt;&gt; Kunpa: YOU CLIMBED THIS HUGE

00:09:53.887 --> 00:09:55.356
TREE ALL BY YOURSELF.

00:09:55.356 --> 00:09:56.292
WE CAN’T JUST CALL YOU

00:09:56.292 --> 00:09:57.595
NAAKIM ANYMORE!

00:09:57.595 --> 00:09:59.231
YOU’RE NAAKIM THE TREE‐CLIMBER!

00:09:59.231 --> 00:10:01.670
&gt;&gt; NAAKIM THE TREE‐CLIMBER!

00:10:01.670 --> 00:10:02.204
&gt;&gt; Naakim: THANKS.

00:10:02.204 --> 00:10:05.276
[students laughing]

00:10:12.792 --> 00:10:14.963
&gt;&gt; Yoko: [chuckles]

00:10:14.963 --> 00:10:17.033
&gt;&gt; Nia: THE SPIRAL NEMESIS WILL

00:10:17.033 --> 00:10:17.869
BRING ABOUT THE DESTRUCTION OF

00:10:17.869 --> 00:10:18.770
THIS UNIVERSE.

00:10:18.770 --> 00:10:21.108
WE ANTI‐SPIRALS EXIST TO PREVENT

00:10:21.108 --> 00:10:23.847
THAT FROM HAPPENING.

00:10:23.847 --> 00:10:25.651
THE GROWING HUMAN POPULATION

00:10:25.651 --> 00:10:26.987
AND ITS CIVILIZATIONS WILL

00:10:26.987 --> 00:10:28.289
ADVANCE EXPLOSIVELY.

00:10:28.289 --> 00:10:30.093
AND SO WE WILL DESTROY YOU

00:10:30.093 --> 00:10:30.928
BEFORE THAT CAN HAPPEN.

00:10:30.928 --> 00:10:32.164
&gt;&gt; Simon: THAT’S WHAT THE

00:10:32.164 --> 00:10:33.332
HUMANITY ANNIHILATION SYSTEM IS?

00:10:33.332 --> 00:10:35.003
THAT MECHA EARLIER TODAY?

00:10:35.003 --> 00:10:36.272
&gt;&gt; Nia: IN THREE WEEKS,

00:10:36.272 --> 00:10:37.675
THE MOON WILL BREAK AWAY FROM

00:10:37.675 --> 00:10:38.677
ITS ORBIT AND DIRECTLY IMPACT

00:10:38.677 --> 00:10:40.079
THE EARTH, AND THAT WILL BE

00:10:40.079 --> 00:10:40.915
THE END OF IT.

00:10:40.915 --> 00:10:42.819
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: IN RESPONSE TO THIS

00:10:42.819 --> 00:10:44.656
NEWS, THE NEW GOVERNMENT PRESSED

00:10:44.656 --> 00:10:45.624
CHARGES AGAINST FORMER

00:10:45.624 --> 00:10:46.392
COMMANDER SIMON.

00:10:46.392 --> 00:10:48.362
AS A RESULT OF HIS TRIAL TODAY,

00:10:48.362 --> 00:10:50.166
HE WAS SENTENCED TO DEATH.

00:10:50.166 --> 00:10:51.368
CITIZENS AROUND THE WORLD

00:10:51.368 --> 00:10:52.003
WILL BE EVACUATED...

00:10:52.003 --> 00:10:53.139
&gt;&gt; TEACHER!

00:10:53.139 --> 00:10:54.408
&gt;&gt; Yoko: DON’T BE AFRAID.

00:10:54.408 --> 00:10:55.811
LET’S BELIEVE IN THE NEW

00:10:55.811 --> 00:10:57.214
GOVERNMENT.

00:10:57.214 --> 00:10:58.984
WHAT THE HECK ARE THEY DOING?

00:10:58.984 --> 00:11:04.228
WHAT ARE THEY UP TO?

00:11:04.228 --> 00:11:05.698
&gt;&gt; Principal: LISTEN, EVERYONE!

00:11:05.698 --> 00:11:06.867
A GUNBOAT WILL BE HERE

00:11:06.867 --> 00:11:08.269
IN AN HOUR TO EVACUATE US.

00:11:08.269 --> 00:11:09.338
LOOK AROUND.

00:11:09.338 --> 00:11:10.273
MAKE SURE YOU HAVEN’T

00:11:10.273 --> 00:11:11.275
FORGOTTEN ANYTHING.

00:11:11.275 --> 00:11:12.945
&gt;&gt; MISS YOMAKO!

00:11:12.945 --> 00:11:13.914
PLEASE, IT’S OUR MAOSHA!

00:11:13.914 --> 00:11:14.849
&gt;&gt; WE CAN’T FIND MAOSHA

00:11:14.849 --> 00:11:16.318
ANYWHERE!

00:11:16.318 --> 00:11:17.153
&gt;&gt; Yoko: WHAT?!

00:11:17.153 --> 00:11:17.855
&gt;&gt; Naakim: I CAN GO LOOK

00:11:17.855 --> 00:11:18.189
FOR HER!

00:11:18.189 --> 00:11:19.258
&gt;&gt; Yoko: NO, NAAKIM.

00:11:19.258 --> 00:11:20.126
YOU STAY HERE.

00:11:20.126 --> 00:11:21.262
&gt;&gt; Kunpa: HEY, I BET SHE’S UP

00:11:21.262 --> 00:11:22.197
IN THE LIGHTHOUSE!

00:11:22.197 --> 00:11:23.734
&gt;&gt; Geki: WHENEVER ANYTHING BAD

00:11:23.734 --> 00:11:24.903
HAPPENS, SHE RUNS UP THERE

00:11:24.903 --> 00:11:26.272
AND CRIES.

00:11:26.272 --> 00:11:27.808
[Maosha sobbing]

00:11:27.808 --> 00:11:29.979
&gt;&gt; Maosha: I CAN’T GO.

00:11:29.979 --> 00:11:31.448
I’M A BIG, FAT LIAR.

00:11:31.448 --> 00:11:33.185
I CAN’T GO WITH NAAKIM.

00:11:33.185 --> 00:11:34.454
I CAN’T GO!

00:11:34.454 --> 00:11:40.868
I JUST CAN’T.

00:11:40.868 --> 00:11:42.370
OH!

00:11:42.370 --> 00:11:43.707
&gt;&gt; Dashah: DASHAH!

00:11:43.707 --> 00:11:44.842
[Maosha screams]

00:11:44.842 --> 00:11:46.813
&gt;&gt; Yoko: OH!

00:11:46.813 --> 00:11:51.690
THOSE FOOTSTEPS ARE‐‐

00:11:51.690 --> 00:11:52.457
&gt;&gt; Gamel: NOW LISTEN AND LISTEN

00:11:52.457 --> 00:11:53.827
UP GOOD!

00:11:53.827 --> 00:11:55.096
CAN YOU HEAR ME?

00:11:55.096 --> 00:11:56.165
IF THIS KID’S LIFE MEANS

00:11:56.165 --> 00:11:58.169
ANYTHING TO YOU, YOU’LL HAND

00:11:58.169 --> 00:11:59.806
OVER ALL THE FOOD ON THE ISLAND!

00:11:59.806 --> 00:12:01.075
[Maosha whimpering]

00:12:01.075 --> 00:12:02.043
&gt;&gt; MAOSHA!

00:12:02.043 --> 00:12:03.246
&gt;&gt; Principal: WHAT GOOD DO YOU

00:12:03.246 --> 00:12:04.147
THINK THIS WILL DO?

00:12:04.147 --> 00:12:04.949
IF YOU DON’T EVACUATE WITH

00:12:04.949 --> 00:12:06.485
EVERYONE, THE MOON’LL FALL

00:12:06.485 --> 00:12:07.020
ON YOU!

00:12:07.020 --> 00:12:07.989
&gt;&gt; Gamel: HEH HEH!

00:12:07.989 --> 00:12:09.826
MY PARTNER HERE AND I ARE

00:12:09.826 --> 00:12:10.360
WANTED MEN!

00:12:10.360 --> 00:12:11.997
THEY’D ARREST US IF WE WENT TO

00:12:11.997 --> 00:12:12.798
ONE OF THEIR SHELTERS.

00:12:12.798 --> 00:12:14.001
SO WE THOUGHT IT’D BE SMARTER

00:12:14.001 --> 00:12:15.103
FOR US TO LOAD OUR GUNMEN WITH

00:12:15.103 --> 00:12:17.407
FOOD AND SUPPLIES AND JUST HIDE

00:12:17.407 --> 00:12:18.744
OUT SOMEPLACE!

00:12:18.744 --> 00:12:19.779
&gt;&gt; Dashah: LOOK, DO YOU CARE

00:12:19.779 --> 00:12:21.382
WHAT HAPPENS TO THIS KID,

00:12:21.382 --> 00:12:22.017
OR DON’T YOU?!

00:12:22.017 --> 00:12:26.860
YOU’RE DEAD MEAT EITHER WAY!

00:12:26.860 --> 00:12:27.895
&gt;&gt; Yoko: UNH!

00:12:27.895 --> 00:12:29.331
[class screams]

00:12:29.331 --> 00:12:30.734
&gt;&gt; Naakim: STOP IT!

00:12:30.734 --> 00:12:36.045
&gt;&gt; Dashah: DASHAH!

00:12:36.045 --> 00:12:39.752
&gt;&gt; Yoko: [gasps]

00:12:39.752 --> 00:12:41.990
THEY’RE GONNA PAY.

00:12:41.990 --> 00:12:44.896
♪ ROW, ROW, FIGHT THE POWER ♪ ♪

00:12:49.471 --> 00:12:52.745
♪ ROW, ROW, FIGHT THE POWER ♪ ♪

00:13:11.415 --> 00:13:13.419
[Dashah laughs]

00:13:13.419 --> 00:13:14.555
&gt;&gt; Dashah: WHAT’S WRONG?

00:13:14.555 --> 00:13:15.824
&gt;&gt; Gamel: IF YOU DON’T HAND OVER

00:13:15.824 --> 00:13:17.427
YOUR FOOD, THIS POOR LITTLE KID

00:13:17.427 --> 00:13:18.930
IS A GONER!

00:13:18.930 --> 00:13:20.433
&gt;&gt; Dashah: DASHAH!

00:13:20.433 --> 00:13:22.872
&gt;&gt; MAOSHA, NO!

00:13:22.872 --> 00:13:26.078
&gt;&gt; MAOSHA’S GONNA GET EATEN!

00:13:30.821 --> 00:13:32.357
&gt;&gt; Gamel: WHAT’S THAT?

00:13:32.357 --> 00:13:34.027
&gt;&gt; Dashah: WHAT’S GOIN’ ON?

00:13:40.273 --> 00:13:41.943
[all gasp]

00:13:41.943 --> 00:13:47.287
[Maosha screaming]

00:13:47.287 --> 00:13:50.426
&gt;&gt; Dashah: DASHAH!

00:13:50.426 --> 00:13:52.865
&gt;&gt; MAOSHA!

00:13:52.865 --> 00:13:54.067
MY LITTLE GIRL.

00:13:54.067 --> 00:13:55.336
&gt;&gt; MAOSHA!

00:13:55.336 --> 00:13:57.207
&gt;&gt; Maosha: MISS YOMAKO...

00:13:57.207 --> 00:14:02.150
IS THAT YOU?

00:14:02.150 --> 00:14:03.820
&gt;&gt; Yoko: STAY BACK, KIDS.

00:14:03.820 --> 00:14:05.958
&gt;&gt; OH!

00:14:05.958 --> 00:14:07.962
&gt;&gt; Naakim: I KNEW IT!

00:14:07.962 --> 00:14:10.366
THIS IS HER IN OUR TEXTBOOK!

00:14:10.366 --> 00:14:11.603
&gt;&gt; Dashah: AND JUST WHO THE

00:14:11.603 --> 00:14:12.972
HELL ARE YOU?

00:14:12.972 --> 00:14:14.909
&gt;&gt; Yoko: I AM A TEACHER.

00:14:14.909 --> 00:14:16.513
&gt;&gt; Dashah: DON’T MAKE ME LAUGH!

00:14:16.513 --> 00:14:18.382
LOOK AT WHAT YOU DID TO MY BRO!

00:14:18.382 --> 00:14:19.251
&gt;&gt; Yoko: THIS WILL BE

00:14:19.251 --> 00:14:20.053
ON THE TEST.

00:14:20.053 --> 00:14:21.255
PAY CLOSE ATTENTION.

00:14:21.255 --> 00:14:22.958
YOU DON’T WRECK BUILDINGS.

00:14:22.958 --> 00:14:25.029
&gt;&gt; Dashah: DASHAH!

00:14:31.308 --> 00:14:32.845
&gt;&gt; Yoko: YOU DON’T TAKE

00:14:32.845 --> 00:14:33.547
CHILDREN HOSTAGE.

00:14:33.547 --> 00:14:39.892
&gt;&gt; Naakim: [gasps]

00:14:39.892 --> 00:14:41.563
&gt;&gt; Yoko: AND YOU DON’T THREATEN

00:14:41.563 --> 00:14:46.973
PEOPLE WITH VIOLENCE.

00:14:46.973 --> 00:14:50.046
OKAY, CLASS DISMISSED.

00:14:56.024 --> 00:14:57.026
LOOKS LIKE YOU FAIL.

00:14:57.026 --> 00:14:59.431
[Dashah and Gamel whimper]

00:14:59.431 --> 00:15:01.101
[Maosha sniffles]

00:15:01.101 --> 00:15:03.005
&gt;&gt; Maosha: I’M SORRY, NAAKIM.

00:15:03.005 --> 00:15:05.209
I WAS THE ONE WHO PUT YOUR BAG

00:15:05.209 --> 00:15:05.944
UP THERE.

00:15:05.944 --> 00:15:06.546
&gt;&gt; Naakim: HUH?

00:15:06.546 --> 00:15:07.548
&gt;&gt; Maosha: I’M A REALLY GOOD

00:15:07.548 --> 00:15:08.917
TREE CLIMBER, SO I THOUGHT I’D

00:15:08.917 --> 00:15:09.986
BLAME KUNPA AND HIS FRIENDS,

00:15:09.986 --> 00:15:11.990
AND THEN I’D GET IT FOR YOU,

00:15:11.990 --> 00:15:12.490
AND YOU’D‐‐

00:15:12.490 --> 00:15:13.894
&gt;&gt; Naakim: MAOSHA.

00:15:13.894 --> 00:15:14.896
&gt;&gt; Maosha: I SWEAR, I DIDN’T

00:15:14.896 --> 00:15:16.231
KNOW HOW MUCH THE BAG MEANT

00:15:16.231 --> 00:15:16.966
TO YOU.

00:15:16.966 --> 00:15:22.545
NAAKIM, I’M SORRY.

00:15:22.545 --> 00:15:24.080
&gt;&gt; Naakim: LET’S ALL RUN AWAY,

00:15:24.080 --> 00:15:24.916
MAOSHA.

00:15:24.916 --> 00:15:25.584
[students laughing]

00:15:25.584 --> 00:15:30.994
&gt;&gt; Maosha: NAAKIM.

00:15:30.994 --> 00:15:33.365
[beeping]

00:15:33.365 --> 00:15:34.669
&gt;&gt; Yoko: A MESSAGE?

00:15:34.669 --> 00:15:36.004
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: YOKO.

00:15:36.004 --> 00:15:37.440
I WANT YOU TO COME BACK

00:15:37.440 --> 00:15:38.677
TO KAMINA CITY AND JOIN US

00:15:38.677 --> 00:15:40.012
ON THE ARC‐GURREN.

00:15:40.012 --> 00:15:41.950
THE EARTH IS GOING TO DESTROYED,

00:15:41.950 --> 00:15:43.085
SO HURRY.

00:15:43.085 --> 00:15:44.020
YOU ARE SOMEONE WHO OUGHT

00:15:44.020 --> 00:15:44.989
TO SURVIVE!

00:15:44.989 --> 00:15:45.958
PLEASE!

00:15:45.958 --> 00:15:48.062
CONTACT ME IMMEDIATELY!

00:15:48.062 --> 00:15:49.164
PLEASE!

00:15:49.164 --> 00:15:51.201
CONTACT ME IMMEDIATELY...

00:15:51.201 --> 00:15:52.203
&gt;&gt; Yoko: SO THIS IS YOUR

00:15:52.203 --> 00:15:54.107
"POLITICS," HUH?

00:15:54.107 --> 00:15:56.713
WHAT A STUPID JOKE.

00:15:56.713 --> 00:15:59.084
[students chatter sadly]

00:15:59.084 --> 00:16:01.421
&gt;&gt; ARE YOU LEAVING, MISS YOMAKO?

00:16:01.421 --> 00:16:02.157
&gt;&gt; Naakim: I KNEW IT.

00:16:02.157 --> 00:16:04.161
YOU’RE YOKO FROM OUR TEXTBOOK!

00:16:04.161 --> 00:16:05.263
&gt;&gt; Yoko: NO.

00:16:05.263 --> 00:16:06.599
NO MATTER WHAT HAPPENS,

00:16:06.599 --> 00:16:07.735
I PROMISE, I’LL ALWAYS BE

00:16:07.735 --> 00:16:09.070
YOUR MISS YOMAKO.

00:16:09.070 --> 00:16:11.441
&gt;&gt; Kunpa: YEAH, THAT’S RIGHT!

00:16:11.441 --> 00:16:13.045
YOU’RE KOREHANA ISLAND’S

00:16:13.045 --> 00:16:14.114
MISS YOMAKO, YEAH!

00:16:14.114 --> 00:16:16.118
&gt;&gt; Naakim: MISS YOMAKO!

00:16:16.118 --> 00:16:17.453
&gt;&gt; Yoko: I’LL GO GET IT BACK

00:16:17.453 --> 00:16:18.422
FOR YOU.

00:16:18.422 --> 00:16:19.391
I’LL SAVE THE PURE BLUE SKY THAT

00:16:19.391 --> 00:16:21.295
YOU KIDS LOVE.

00:16:21.295 --> 00:16:24.334
&gt;&gt; MISS YOMAKO!

00:16:24.334 --> 00:16:26.038
&gt;&gt; Yoko: WHEN I GET BACK, I’LL

00:16:26.038 --> 00:16:27.140
HAND OUT YOUR REPORT CARDS.

00:16:27.140 --> 00:16:29.512
&gt;&gt; HUH?

00:16:29.512 --> 00:16:32.417
[Yoko chuckles]

00:16:32.417 --> 00:16:37.393
[students shouting]

00:16:37.393 --> 00:16:39.130
&gt;&gt; Naakim: COME BACK SOON,

00:16:39.130 --> 00:16:39.999
MISS YOMAKO!

00:16:39.999 --> 00:16:41.101
WE’LL BE WAITING FOR YOU!

00:16:41.101 --> 00:16:43.707
THAT’S A PROMISE!

00:16:46.411 --> 00:16:48.750
&gt;&gt; I’LL MISS YOU!

00:16:48.750 --> 00:16:51.054
&gt;&gt; TAKE CARE NOW!

00:16:58.035 --> 00:17:00.106
&gt;&gt; Yoko: OHH!

00:17:09.725 --> 00:17:11.194
&gt;&gt; Kittan: DAMN IT!

00:17:11.194 --> 00:17:12.263
IT’S NEVER‐ENDING!

00:17:12.263 --> 00:17:13.767
&gt;&gt; Yoko: WORKING HARD, KITTAN?

00:17:13.767 --> 00:17:14.434
&gt;&gt; Kittan: WHAT?

00:17:14.434 --> 00:17:16.071
YOKO, IS THAT YOU?

00:17:16.071 --> 00:17:18.142
&gt;&gt; Yoko: WHERE’S SIMON?

00:17:18.142 --> 00:17:19.211
&gt;&gt; Kittan: HE’S STILL IN THAT

00:17:19.211 --> 00:17:20.112
PRISON DOWN THERE!

00:17:20.112 --> 00:17:21.081
&gt;&gt; Yoko: THEN I’LL LEAVE OUR

00:17:21.081 --> 00:17:22.651
"FRIENDS" BACK THERE TO YOU!

00:17:22.651 --> 00:17:23.553
&gt;&gt; Kittan: HEY, WAIT JUST

00:17:23.553 --> 00:17:24.589
A MINUTE!

00:17:24.589 --> 00:17:25.624
YOU SHOW UP OUT OF NOWHERE AND

00:17:25.624 --> 00:17:27.795
STEAL THE RESCUE FOR YOURSELF?!

00:17:27.795 --> 00:17:30.166
AW, CRAP!

00:17:30.166 --> 00:17:31.235
MAN, THERE’S STILL A FEW

00:17:31.235 --> 00:17:36.311
LEFT, HUH?

00:17:36.311 --> 00:17:40.621
IT’S YOU GUYS!

00:17:40.621 --> 00:17:41.689
&gt;&gt; Yoko: WERE YOU JUST GONNA SIT

00:17:41.689 --> 00:17:43.693
QUIETLY AND ROT AWAY IN HERE?

00:17:43.693 --> 00:17:45.196
&gt;&gt; Simon: YOKO, WHERE HAVE YOU

00:17:45.196 --> 00:17:46.198
BEEN HIDING OUT?

00:17:46.198 --> 00:17:47.233
&gt;&gt; Yoko: I’LL TELL YOU ABOUT IT

00:17:47.233 --> 00:17:48.035
SOME OTHER TIME.

00:17:48.035 --> 00:17:49.805
IF WHAT NIA SAID IS TRUE,

00:17:49.805 --> 00:17:51.609
WE’RE IN BIG TROUBLE.

00:17:51.609 --> 00:17:53.245
THE MOON IS FALLING.

00:17:53.245 --> 00:17:54.515
THE SURFACE AND UNDERGROUND WILL

00:17:54.515 --> 00:17:55.751
BOTH BE DESTROYED.

00:17:55.751 --> 00:17:57.053
THERE’S NOWHERE TO RUN.

00:17:57.053 --> 00:17:58.088
&gt;&gt; Simon: AND IT SOUNDS LIKE

00:17:58.088 --> 00:17:58.757
THERE’S AN AMBUSH WAITING

00:17:58.757 --> 00:17:59.725
FOR THEM.

00:17:59.725 --> 00:18:01.328
OUR BACK’S AGAINST THE WALL.

00:18:01.328 --> 00:18:02.564
&gt;&gt; Yoko: MAYBE SO, BUT FINDING

00:18:02.564 --> 00:18:04.167
A WAY OUT OF NO‐WIN SITUATIONS

00:18:04.167 --> 00:18:06.204
IS TEAM GURREN’S SPECIALTY.

00:18:06.204 --> 00:18:08.208
&gt;&gt; Simon: YEAH, IT IS, ISN’T IT?

00:18:08.208 --> 00:18:09.077
&gt;&gt; Viral: I SEE YOU STILL HAVE

00:18:09.077 --> 00:18:11.248
AS MUCH SPUNK AS EVER, WOMAN.

00:18:11.248 --> 00:18:12.483
&gt;&gt; Yoko: VIRAL?!

00:18:12.483 --> 00:18:18.395
&gt;&gt; Simon: YOKO, YOUR GUN.

00:18:18.395 --> 00:18:20.534
&gt;&gt; Viral: WHAT ARE YOU UP TO?

00:18:20.534 --> 00:18:21.536
&gt;&gt; Simon: YOU HEARD WHAT

00:18:21.536 --> 00:18:22.203
SHE SAID.

00:18:22.203 --> 00:18:24.274
TEAM GURREN’S GONNA SAVE EVERY

00:18:24.274 --> 00:18:26.144
LIVING THING ON THE SURFACE.

00:18:26.144 --> 00:18:26.846
&gt;&gt; Viral: REALLY?

00:18:26.846 --> 00:18:27.615
HOW?

00:18:27.615 --> 00:18:29.184
&gt;&gt; Simon: OH, THAT’S EASY.

00:18:29.184 --> 00:18:30.152
WE’LL STOP THE MOON.

00:18:30.152 --> 00:18:31.421
&gt;&gt; Viral: ARE YOU SERIOUS?

00:18:31.421 --> 00:18:32.758
&gt;&gt; Simon: VIRAL, YOU SHOULD KNOW

00:18:32.758 --> 00:18:33.793
BETTER THAN ANYONE THAT I’M

00:18:33.793 --> 00:18:34.595
ALWAYS SERIOUS.

00:18:34.595 --> 00:18:36.231
JUST WHO THE HELL DO YOU

00:18:36.231 --> 00:18:37.133
THINK I AM?

00:18:37.133 --> 00:18:38.703
&gt;&gt; Viral: I KNOW WHO YOU ARE.

00:18:38.703 --> 00:18:40.206
YOU’RE THAT FOOL

00:18:40.206 --> 00:18:41.241
FROM TEAM GURREN.

00:18:47.186 --> 00:18:49.692
&gt;&gt; Simon: OH!

00:18:49.692 --> 00:18:51.529
GUYS?

00:18:51.529 --> 00:18:52.531
&gt;&gt; Kittan: YOU’RE A FREE MAN

00:18:52.531 --> 00:18:53.900
AGAIN.

00:18:53.900 --> 00:18:55.102
&gt;&gt; Viral: WELL, HERE’S A BUNCH

00:18:55.102 --> 00:18:56.238
OF FAMILIAR FACES.

00:18:56.238 --> 00:18:57.641
&gt;&gt; Balinbow: HEY, THAT’S‐‐

00:18:57.641 --> 00:18:58.710
WHAT HE DOING HERE?

00:18:58.710 --> 00:18:59.712
&gt;&gt; Simon: RIGHT NOW WE NEED

00:18:59.712 --> 00:19:01.214
EVERY GOOD GUNMEN PILOT WE

00:19:01.214 --> 00:19:02.450
CAN GET.

00:19:02.450 --> 00:19:03.553
&gt;&gt; Kittan: WE GONNA DO IT?

00:19:03.553 --> 00:19:04.254
&gt;&gt; Simon: YEAH.

00:19:04.254 --> 00:19:05.757
IF WE DON’T STOP THAT THING,

00:19:05.757 --> 00:19:07.327
EARTH HAS NO FUTURE.

00:19:07.327 --> 00:19:09.130
&gt;&gt; Kittan: YOU KNOW ABOUT THAT?

00:19:09.130 --> 00:19:10.232
THAT SAVES A LOT OF TIME.

00:19:10.232 --> 00:19:12.136
LISTEN UP, BOZOS!

00:19:12.136 --> 00:19:13.272
WE’RE GONNA SMASH UP THAT

00:19:13.272 --> 00:19:16.178
BIG‐ASS CEILING UP THERE!

00:19:16.178 --> 00:19:18.382
&gt;&gt; YEAH!

00:19:18.382 --> 00:19:20.687
[Boota grunting]

00:19:20.687 --> 00:19:22.457
&gt;&gt; Simon: BOOTA, WOW,

00:19:22.457 --> 00:19:23.192
YOU’RE STILL ALIVE!

00:19:23.192 --> 00:19:24.227
&gt;&gt; Yoko: WELL, THAT MEANS THE

00:19:24.227 --> 00:19:26.566
GANG’S ALL HERE.

00:19:26.566 --> 00:19:29.337
BOY, BOOTA, YOU’RE AS TINY

00:19:29.337 --> 00:19:32.811
AS EVER.

00:19:32.811 --> 00:19:33.880
&gt;&gt; Leyte: IT’S A PRESENT

00:19:33.880 --> 00:19:35.282
FROM LEERON.

00:19:35.282 --> 00:19:37.220
WE BOOSTED ITS OUTPUT, TOO.

00:19:37.220 --> 00:19:38.823
I’LL LAUNCH THE REST OF ’EM INTO

00:19:38.823 --> 00:19:40.493
SPACE ON THAT ROCKET GUNMEN.

00:19:40.493 --> 00:19:42.363
&gt;&gt; Viral: YOU’RE PERSISTENT,

00:19:42.363 --> 00:19:43.198
I’LL GIVE YOU THAT,

00:19:43.198 --> 00:19:44.735
YOU AND THIS THING.

00:19:44.735 --> 00:19:45.804
&gt;&gt; Simon: CARE TO PILOT

00:19:45.804 --> 00:19:46.606
"THIS THING"?

00:19:46.606 --> 00:19:47.407
&gt;&gt; Viral: WHAT’S THAT?

00:19:47.407 --> 00:19:48.275
&gt;&gt; Simon: YOU SAID YOU WERE

00:19:48.275 --> 00:19:49.277
SUPPOSED TO OBSERVE HUMANITY’S

00:19:49.277 --> 00:19:50.279
FATE, RIGHT?

00:19:50.279 --> 00:19:51.682
YOU’LL HAVE A FRONT‐ROW SEAT

00:19:51.682 --> 00:19:53.318
HERE IN GURREN’S COCKPIT.

00:19:53.318 --> 00:19:55.189
&gt;&gt; Viral: GURREN LAGANN, HUH?

00:19:55.189 --> 00:19:56.358
EVEN WITH THE HUMILIATION I’VE

00:19:56.358 --> 00:19:57.728
SUFFERED AT ITS HANDS...

