ALL RIGHT, YOU’RE ON.

00:20:01.836 --> 00:20:02.905
&gt;&gt; Simon: YOU BETTER GET READY,

00:20:02.905 --> 00:20:04.809
’CAUSE THIS BABY PACKS A PUNCH.

