00:20:24.615 --> 00:20:26.251
THE DAI‐GUNMEN CONFIGURATION WAS

00:20:26.251 --> 00:20:27.386
ORIGINALLY DESIGNED FOR

00:20:27.386 --> 00:20:28.556
ATMOSPHERIC REENTRY.

00:20:28.556 --> 00:20:29.658
&gt;&gt; Jorgun: ATMOSPHERIC?

00:20:29.658 --> 00:20:30.527
WHAT THAT?

