CAN YOU EAT IT?

00:20:31.662 --> 00:20:32.831
&gt;&gt; Leyte: LOOK, ALL IT MEANS IS

00:20:32.831 --> 00:20:34.434
THAT YOUR GUNMEN CAN FIGHT

00:20:34.434 --> 00:20:34.902
IN SPACE.

00:20:34.902 --> 00:20:36.338
&gt;&gt; Balinbow: ALL RIGHT!

00:20:36.338 --> 00:20:37.407
WE DO THAT!

00:20:37.407 --> 00:20:39.411
&gt;&gt; Leyte: WE’RE COUNTING ON YOU.

00:20:39.411 --> 00:20:41.616
GOOD LUCK.

00:20:41.616 --> 00:20:42.618
[Yoko grunting]

00:20:42.618 --> 00:20:47.761
&gt;&gt; Yoko: OH!

00:20:47.761 --> 00:20:50.433
WE’LL GET IT BACK,

00:20:50.433 --> 00:20:52.370
A CAREFREE WORLD

00:20:52.370 --> 00:20:53.540
WHERE KIDS CAN LIVE AND PLAY

00:20:53.540 --> 00:20:56.979
UNDER THE SUN.

00:20:56.979 --> 00:20:58.583
&gt;&gt; Gimmy: DAMN IT, WE’RE NOT

00:20:58.583 --> 00:20:59.350
EVEN DENTING THOSE THINGS!

00:20:59.350 --> 00:21:00.921
&gt;&gt; Darry: HEY, CALM DOWN, GIMMY.

00:21:00.921 --> 00:21:02.457
WE CAN’T LOSE OUR CONCENTRATION!

00:21:02.457 --> 00:21:03.760
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: DAMAGE?

00:21:03.760 --> 00:21:04.728
&gt;&gt; Guinble: SEVERE DAMAGE TO

00:21:04.728 --> 00:21:05.964
