THEN ALL THAT WE’VE DONE WILL

00:21:22.296 --> 00:21:25.002
HAVE BEEN FOR‐‐WHAT HAPPENED?!

00:21:25.002 --> 00:21:26.506
&gt;&gt; Lordgenome: SPIRAL POWER

00:21:26.506 --> 00:21:27.373
IS FALLING.

00:21:27.373 --> 00:21:28.510
ALL SPIRAL LIFE‐FORM ENERGY

00:21:28.510 --> 00:21:30.012
READINGS ARE RAPIDLY WEAKENING.

00:21:30.012 --> 00:21:31.014
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: WHAT DID YOU SAY?

00:21:31.014 --> 00:21:32.350
&gt;&gt; Kinon: THE PEOPLE ONBOARD

00:21:32.350 --> 00:21:33.318
ARE WORRIED.

