THEY’RE WORRIED BECAUSE OF

00:21:34.955 --> 00:21:35.724
THE ATTACK.

00:21:35.724 --> 00:21:37.928
AND NOT JUST THE CITIZENS.

00:21:37.928 --> 00:21:39.565
US TOO.

00:21:39.565 --> 00:21:41.067
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: IT CAN’T BE.

00:21:41.067 --> 00:21:42.704
HOW COULD A MACHINE’S POWER BE

00:21:42.704 --> 00:21:45.442
INFLUENCED BY HUMAN EMOTIONS?

00:21:45.442 --> 00:21:48.850
ALTHOUGH THAT MIGHT BE THE CASE.

00:21:48.850 --> 00:21:50.921
IF THAT’S TRUE, HAVE I REACHED

00:21:50.921 --> 00:21:53.560
MY LIMIT?

00:21:53.560 --> 00:21:54.460
&gt;&gt; Simon: ROSSIU!

00:21:54.460 --> 00:21:55.329
DON’T GIVE UP!

00:21:55.329 --> 00:22:00.607
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: [gasps]

00:22:00.607 --> 00:22:02.076
CAN’T BE.

00:22:02.076 --> 00:22:03.546
SIMON!

00:22:03.546 --> 00:22:04.548
&gt;&gt; Simon: THE INSTANT YOU GIVE

00:22:04.548 --> 00:22:06.084
UP, IT’S OVER!

00:22:06.084 --> 00:22:07.788
DON’T YOU REMEMBER?

